offChainJsonMetadata.name: LYFINITY - 000
offChainJsonMetadata.description: LYFINITY, a sci-fi short written by Shivani Bhargava and published in honor of Women’s History Month, is a far future look back–from an alien perspective–on the extinction of the human species due to the innovation of a life-extending drug that only works for genetically XX chromosomal humans.
